'''Stationary''' monsters cannot move and usually rely on ranged attacks to harm you. [[Oklob plant]]s and certain [[statue]]s are the most common dangerous stationary monsters. Stationary monsters will automatically have their tile [[exclusion|auto-excluded]] when discovered.

Stationary monsters can never be [[slow]]ed or [[haste]]d and cannot [[blink]] or [[teleport]], even when hit by weapons of [[distortion]] or [[boomerang]]s of [[dispersal (brand)|dispersal]]. They may, however, still be [[banish]]ed by weapons of distortion.

